import React from 'react';
import { AboutContanier } from '../Aboutpage/About.elements';
import { 
    ContactWrap, 
    GetInTouchWrap, 
    GetInTouchHeading,
    GetInTouchText,
    QuickLinkIconWrap,
    QuickLinkWrap,
    QuickLinkIcon,
    QuickLinkIcon2,
    QuickLinkText1,
    QuickLinkText2,
    ContactFromWrap,
    ContactFrom,
    ContactInputWrap,
    TextAreaInput } from './Contact.elements';
import {
    FormInput
} from '../../components/Footer/Footer.elements';

import Imessage from '../../assets/images/imessage.png';
import Phone from '../../assets/images/phone.png';
import PlaceMarker from '../../assets/images/place-marker.png';

const Contact = () => {
    return(
        <AboutContanier>
            <ContactWrap>
                <GetInTouchWrap>
                    <GetInTouchHeading>Get In Touch</GetInTouchHeading>
                    <GetInTouchText>Got a question or query? Weâ€™d love to chat with you about it! You can say hi and get in touch with our carelines teams using the details below.</GetInTouchText>
                    <QuickLinkWrap>
                        <QuickLinkIconWrap>
                            <QuickLinkIcon src={Imessage} />
                            <QuickLinkText1>peakprime@gmail.com</QuickLinkText1>
                        </QuickLinkIconWrap>
                        <QuickLinkIconWrap>
                            <QuickLinkIcon src={Phone} />
                            <QuickLinkText1>+919611478337</QuickLinkText1>
                        </QuickLinkIconWrap>
                        <QuickLinkIconWrap>
                            <QuickLinkIcon2 src={PlaceMarker} />
                            <QuickLinkText2>Valgevase 13, 10414 Tallinn, Estonia</QuickLinkText2>
                        </QuickLinkIconWrap>
                    </QuickLinkWrap>
                </GetInTouchWrap>
                <ContactFromWrap>
                    <ContactFrom>
                        <GetInTouchHeading>Come say hi</GetInTouchHeading>
                        <ContactInputWrap>
                            <FormInput placeholder="Fullname" />
                            <FormInput placeholder="Email" />
                            <TextAreaInput placeholder="" />
                        </ContactInputWrap>
                    </ContactFrom>
                </ContactFromWrap>
            </ContactWrap>
        </AboutContanier>
    )
}

export default Contact;
